  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  self-identified adult relatives of people diagnosed with bipolar disorder between ages
             18 and 64; up to two persons per family can participate in the multifamily group

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  relative with bipolar disorder will not be involved in the workshop
      </textblock>
